---
---

<section id="servicios" class="py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32 border-t border-white/[0.06] relative">
  <!-- Decorative Background Blur -->
  <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-brand-violet/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none -z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
    <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-brand-indigo uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 font-display">Soluciones Integrales</div>
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white mb-4 font-display">
      Nuestros Servicios Tecnológicos
    </h2>
    <p class="text-zinc-400 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
      Combinamos automatización de procesos con Inteligencia Artificial avanzada para liberar el potencial de tu equipo y modernizar tu infraestructura digital.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Vercel-style 2x2 Grid of Fine-Border Cards -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
    
    <!-- Service 1: Automatización con IA -->
    <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-zinc-950 p-8 hover:border-brand-blue/30 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[300px]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(59,130,246,0.06)_0%,transparent_50%)] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div>
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 text-brand-blue mb-6 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:border-brand-blue/30">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">Automatización de Flujos con IA</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Diseñamos integraciones complejas sin fisuras utilizando plataformas avanzadas como <span class="text-white font-medium">N8N</span> y <span class="text-white font-medium">OpenClaw</span>. Conectamos tus herramientas legadas para eliminar tareas administrativas repetitivas y transferir datos de forma inteligente sin intervención manual.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold text-brand-blue hover:underline gap-1 cursor-pointer">
        <span>Saber más sobre automatización</span>
        <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 2: Oficina Sin Papel -->
    <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-zinc-950 p-8 hover:border-brand-violet/30 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[300px]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(139,92,246,0.06)_0%,transparent_50%)] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div>
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 text-brand-violet mb-6 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:border-brand-violet/30">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">Oficina Sin Papel (Digitalización)</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Migramos tus procesos físicos y montañas de papel analógico a bases de datos estructuradas y flujos de aprobación digital sumamente robustos. Capturamos información en tiempo real de forma segura y eliminamos para siempre el almacenamiento físico en tu oficina.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold text-brand-violet hover:underline gap-1 cursor-pointer">
        <span>Saber más sobre digitalización</span>
        <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 3: Desarrollo Web a Medida -->
    <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-zinc-950 p-8 hover:border-brand-cyan/30 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[300px]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(6,182,212,0.06)_0%,transparent_50%)] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div>
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 text-brand-cyan mb-6 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:border-brand-cyan/30">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 6.75L22.5 12l-5.25 5.25m-10.5 0L1.5 12l5.25-5.25m7.5-3l-4.5 16.5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">Desarrollo Web a Medida</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Diseñamos y programamos portales corporativos y aplicaciones web de rendimiento ultra rápido usando frameworks de última generación como <span class="text-white font-medium">Astro</span>. Garantizamos la máxima optimización SEO, velocidad de carga insuperable y layouts 100% responsivos adaptados al futuro.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold text-brand-cyan hover:underline gap-1 cursor-pointer">
        <span>Saber más sobre desarrollo</span>
        <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 4: Soporte con IA -->
    <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-white/[0.06] bg-zinc-950 p-8 hover:border-brand-indigo/30 transition-all duration-500 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[300px]">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top,rgba(99,102,241,0.06)_0%,transparent_50%)] opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div>
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-zinc-900 text-brand-indigo mb-6 transition-all duration-300 group-hover:scale-105 group-hover:border-brand-indigo/30">
          <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 8.511c.884.284 1.5 1.128 1.5 2.097v4.286c0 1.136-.847 2.1-1.98 2.193-.3.025-.603.048-.908.069m-12.14-.069C4.83 17.085 4 16.12 4 14.985V10.7c0-.969.615-1.813 1.5-2.097a30.11 30.11 0 0114.75 0m-14.75 0-.078-.023c-.383-.114-.625-.54-.456-.93a10.052 10.052 0 0113.682-5.464c.39.183.518.652.21 1.012l-.242.285a30.11 30.11 0 01-13.116 5.148zM15 11.25a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display">Intermediación y Soporte con IA</h3>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Estructuramos chatbots y asistentes cognitivos capaces de resolver instantáneamente preguntas frecuentes y reclamos de clientes. Nuestra IA cura y clasifica la información exhaustivamente en bases de conocimiento vectoriales antes de transferir casos críticos a agentes humanos de soporte.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-xs font-semibold text-brand-indigo hover:underline gap-1 cursor-pointer">
        <span>Saber más sobre soporte</span>
        <svg class="w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
